comments.name: remarks
comments.value: Attempts to try a teleport, but may not complete the teleport operation (for example, if there are blocks at the destination.)

comments.name: param
comments.value: Location to teleport the entity to.

comments.name: returns
comments.value:
Returns whether the teleport succeeded.
This can fail if the destination chunk is unloaded or if the teleport would result in intersecting with blocks.
